metadata.name: Taiwan X Girls #01   台灣 X女孩們#01
metadata.description:
Taiwan X Girls #01
台灣 X女孩們 #01
台灣 X女の子 #01

1/1  artwork

As a thank you ,
All bidders will receive a  free special  NFT.

Her name is Xu Sijin.(徐思堇)
She is a senior middle school student.
Food Lover .
She have a sweet tooth.


The building in her coat is Taipei 101.
It used to be the tallest building in the world.

Hair accessories are Taiwan's endemic butterfly species "Magellan Birdwing"(珠光鳳蝶),

The big flower in the picture is inspired by Hakka flower cloth(客家花布),

The white flower on the chest is a native species of Phalaenopsis in Taiwan(台灣白花蝴蝶蘭).
Everyone will also call this flower "Taiwan Mammy",


This gallery will feature a series of
Paintings with Taiwan ,
I hope that through this gallery,
Let everyone see each unique cute girl.

---------------------------------------------------------

*私の作品を支持してくださった方々に感謝を込めて
この絵のオークションに参加してくださった方々全員に、未公開の特製NFTイラストを差し上げます。
